column2: SELECT    s.specObjID,   s.objID,   s.z,   gse.lgm_tot_p5# as logmass,      p.cModelMag_g - p.extinction_g as app_g,   p.cModelMag_r - p.extinction_r as app_r,   pz.kcorrG as kcorrG,   pz.kcorrR as kcorrR,   p.petroR5#_r as half_light  into mydb.ForLaura_gse from dbo.SpecPhotoAll AS s   JOIN dbo.PhotoObjAll AS p ON s.objID=p.objID   JOIN dbo.Photoz as pz ON p.objID=pz.objID JOIN dbo.galSpecExtra as gse ON s.specObjID= gse.specObjID WHERE s.z < #      and s.class = &&&
